Description: This package uses minimum and maximum air temperature data from TerraClimate dataset (<http://www.climatologylab.org/terraclimate.html>) calibrated with automatic weather stations (AWS) of of National Meteorological Institute of Brazil (INMET) to make climate zoning (air temperature based) for Brazilian territory.
